eating language / eating directions (eled), the basis for the conlangs found over on robot bugs n frogs (etcha/elvish & elvix), gives us the etymology for AMIMI;

AMAMI = 'two as one'
AMIMI = 'one as two'
with the first referring to two humans or elves 'as one', the second referring to one elf or human and one dreamed agent such as AMIMI or perhaps HATCAT 
